        <tr><td>텍스트형 (4/6 OFF)</td><td>4/1~4/5</td><td style="text-align:right">1,687</td><td style="text-align:right">39</td><td style="text-align:right">2.31%</td><td style="text-align:right">206원</td><td style="text-align:right">8,035</td><td style="text-align:right">0.2%</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="ga-note" style="margin-top:8px">* 이미지형이 CTR 2.69% / CPC 169원으로 효율 최고 · 텍스트형은 4/6부터 OFF 처리</div>
